<lb n="0135a09" ed="T"/>地淫<note place="inline">二合</note>銘鉢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>曳<note place="inline">延結反</note>蹉<note place="inline">倉<g ref="#CB01239">𭇎</g>反九</note>薩嚩羯磨素
